title: sapping sting
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

With a word and a gesture, you sap the vitality of one creature you can see within 30 feet. If the target cannot physically resist your magic, they suffer some [[necrotic damage|damage type]] and are weakened for one or two seconds, which may cause them to fall prone or drop what they are holding.